  <entry>
    <title>Github Pages + Hexo 搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="/2021/10/14/2021101401/"/>
    <url>/2021/10/14/2021101401/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、搭建Github-Pages"><a href="#一、搭建Github-Pages" class="headerlink" title="一、搭建Github Pages"></a>一、搭建Github Pages</h1><h3 id="1、新建仓库"><a href="#1、新建仓库" class="headerlink" title="1、新建仓库"></a>1、新建仓库</h3><img src="/2021/10/14/2021101401/1.png" class=""></br></br><div class="note note-info">            <p>Repository name建议使用用户名.github.io</br></p>          </div><img src="/2021/10/14/2021101401/2.png" class=""></br></br><h3 id="2、选择主题"><a href="#2、选择主题" class="headerlink" title="2、选择主题"></a>2、选择主题</h3><img src="/2021/10/14/2021101401/3.png" class=""></br></br><h3 id="3、地址栏访问"><a href="#3、地址栏访问" class="headerlink" title="3、地址栏访问"></a>3、地址栏访问</h3><img src="/2021/10/14/2021101401/4.png" class=""></br></br><h1 id="二、搭建Hexo博客"><a href="#二、搭建Hexo博客" class="headerlink" title="二、搭建Hexo博客"></a>二、搭建Hexo博客</h1><h3 id="1、安装Hexo"><a href="#1、安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="1、安装Hexo"></a>1、安装Hexo</h3><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">npm install -g hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、Hexo初始化"><a href="#2、Hexo初始化" class="headerlink" title="2、Hexo初始化"></a>2、Hexo初始化</h3><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">hexo init      <span class="hljs-comment"># 初始化</span><br>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 安装组件</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note note-info">            <p>Hexo博客目录结构：</br></p>          </div><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">|-- <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span><span class="hljs-meta"># 网站文件</span><br>|-- scaffolds<span class="hljs-meta"># 模板</span><br>|-- source<span class="hljs-meta"># 用户资源</span><br>     |-- _post<span class="hljs-meta"># markdown文档</span><br>|-- themes<span class="hljs-meta"># 主题</span><br>|-- _config.yml<span class="hljs-meta"># 网站配置信息</span><br>|-- <span class="hljs-keyword">package</span>.jaon<span class="hljs-meta"># 应用程序信息</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、启动本地服务器预览"><a href="#3、启动本地服务器预览" class="headerlink" title="3、启动本地服务器预览"></a>3、启动本地服务器预览</h3><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo</span> g<span class="hljs-comment"># 生成页面</span><br>hexo s    <span class="hljs-comment"># 启动预览[支持本地热更新]</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4、访问localhost-4000，出现Hexo默认页面，安装成功"><a href="#4、访问localhost-4000，出现Hexo默认页面，安装成功" class="headerlink" title="4、访问localhost:4000，出现Hexo默认页面，安装成功"></a>4、访问localhost:4000，出现Hexo默认页面，安装成功</h3><img src="/2021/10/14/2021101401/5.png" class=""></br></br><h1 id="三、部署Hexo到Github-Pages"><a href="#三、部署Hexo到Github-Pages" class="headerlink" title="三、部署Hexo到Github Pages"></a>三、部署Hexo到Github Pages</h1><h3 id="1、安装hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#1、安装hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="1、安装hexo-deployer-git"></a>1、安装hexo-deployer-git</h3><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs ada">npm install hexo-deployer-git <span class="hljs-comment">--save</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、修改-config-yml的deploy部分"><a href="#2、修改-config-yml的deploy部分" class="headerlink" title="2、修改_config.yml的deploy部分"></a>2、修改_config.yml的deploy部分</h3><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">deploy:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  type:</span> git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  repository:</span> https:<span class="hljs-comment">//github.com/用户名/用户名.github.io</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  branch:</span> 分支名<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、将Hexo博客上传部署到Github-Pages"><a href="#3、将Hexo博客上传部署到Github-Pages" class="headerlink" title="3、将Hexo博客上传部署到Github Pages"></a>3、将Hexo博客上传部署到Github Pages</h3><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo d</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4、访问Github域名，出现Hexo博客页面，部署完成"><a href="#4、访问Github域名，出现Hexo博客页面，部署完成" class="headerlink" title="4、访问Github域名，出现Hexo博客页面，部署完成"></a>4、访问Github域名，出现Hexo博客页面，部署完成</h3><h1 id="四、发布文章"><a href="#四、发布文章" class="headerlink" title="四、发布文章"></a>四、发布文章</h1><h3 id="1、创建文章"><a href="#1、创建文章" class="headerlink" title="1、创建文章"></a>1、创建文章</h3><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs haxe">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-type"></span>文章名<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、部署到Github-Pages"><a href="#2、部署到Github-Pages" class="headerlink" title="2、部署到Github Pages"></a>2、部署到Github Pages</h3><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo</span> g<span class="hljs-comment"># 生成页面</span><br>hexo d    <span class="hljs-comment"># 部署发布</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
